    "overview_number": 3,
    "overview_title": "Two-Color Counters",
    "overview_subtitle": "Adding Integers, Part II",
    "overview_description": "In this lesson, students use two-color counters to model positive and negative integers. They identify sums of zero in their model and learn the meaning of the term additive inverse. Using the model, students add integers and compare this strategy to using a number line. They generalize their understanding to write rules to add integers."
  },
